query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from answer AS a1
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow',
'superuser')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('ejs',
'google-chrome',
'iis-6',
'javamail',
'jms',
'mac',
'mapbox',
'python-2.7',
'reference',
'routes',
'selection',
'sqlalchemy',
'tdd')
inner join question AS q1
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 1000
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 100 group by t1.name;
